name: UnofficialPokemonPassportOffice
skdetail:

Invocation Name: unofficial pokemon passport service
des: Pokemon Passport Office is a tool for finding all your favorite pokemon. Pokemon are spread out among generations right now, so finding the right game is difficult. We're here to help. Tell us what Pokemon you're looking for and we'll tell you the last game you could catch the pokemon in and the last game you could play with this pokemon. We are not endorsed by The Pokemon Company, GameFreak, or Nintendo. Nor do we profit from this skill.
